import React from "react";
import styled  from "styled-components";
import {Form }from  "react-bootstrap";

const UserDetailsForm = () => {
 return(
    <Wrapper className="container">
        <Form.Group className="mb-3">
        <Form.Label>Gender</Form.Label>
        <Form.Select >
          <option>Male</option>
          <option>Female</option>
          <option>Other</option>
          <option>Dont want to specify</option>
        </Form.Select>
      </Form.Group>
      <Form.Group className="mb-3">
        <Form.Label>Age</Form.Label>
        
        <Form.Control type="integer" placeholder="Enter your age" />
    
      </Form.Group>
      <Form.Group className="mb-3">
        <Form.Label>Ethinicity</Form.Label>
        <Form.Select >
          <option>British</option>
          <option>Other</option>
        </Form.Select>
      </Form.Group>
      <Form.Group className="mb-3">
        <Form.Label>Laguage</Form.Label>
        <Form.Select >
          <option>English</option>
          <option>Other</option>
        </Form.Select>
      </Form.Group>
      <Form.Group className="mb-3">
        <Form.Label>Personality</Form.Label>
        <Form.Select >
          <option>Extrovert</option>
          <option>Introvert</option>
        </Form.Select>
      </Form.Group>
      <Form.Group className="mb-3">
        <Form.Label>Faculty</Form.Label>
        <Form.Select >
          <option>Science and Technology</option>
          <option>Other</option>
        </Form.Select>
      </Form.Group>
      <Form.Group className="mb-3">
        <Form.Label>Previous Grades</Form.Label>
        <Form.Control type="integer" placeholder="Enter your age" />
      </Form.Group>
      <Form.Group className="mb-3">
        <Form.Label>Discplinary Actions</Form.Label>
        <Form.Control type="integer" placeholder="Enter your age" />
      </Form.Group>
      <Form.Group className="mb-3">
        <Form.Label>Teaching Experience</Form.Label>
        <Form.Control type="integer" placeholder="Enter your age" />
      </Form.Group>
      <Form.Group className="mb-3">
        <Form.Label>Mentoring Experience</Form.Label>
        <Form.Control type="integer" placeholder="Enter your age" />
      </Form.Group>
      <Form.Group className="mb-3">
        <Form.Label>Time Availibility Per week</Form.Label>
        <option>1-5</option>
        <option>5-10</option>
        <option>10+</option>
      </Form.Group>
      <Form.Group className="mb-3">
        <Form.Label>Do you consider studnet having past displinary actions</Form.Label>
        <option>Yes</option>
        <option>No</option>
     </Form.Group>
    </Wrapper>
 )
}
export default UserDetailsForm

const Wrapper= styled.section`
    color: #000;
`
